'''艾瑪·瑪麗亞·沃爾夫哈特'''（{{lang-de|Emma Maria Wolffhardt}}；{{bd|1899年|7月27日|1997年}}）是一名[[德國|德國]]工業化學家。她是[[巴斯夫|巴斯夫]]第一位擁有獨立研究領域的女性化學家<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=https://www.basf.com/global/documents/de/about-us/history/193693_Buch_Anilinerinnen_Screen_final.pdf|title=DIE ANILINERINNEN|website=www.google.com|access-date=2019-05-12|archive-date=2019-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512130105/https://www.basf.com/global/documents/de/about-us/history/193693_Buch_Anilinerinnen_Screen_final.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Publisher2019">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=STWEDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA58|title=Perspectives on Chemical Biography in the 21st Century|author=Cambridge Scholars Publisher|date=14 January 2019|publisher=Cambridge Scholars Publishing|isbn=978-1-5275-2497-2|pages=58–}}</ref><ref name="Tobies1997">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gwR2mmlpgoQC&pg=PA269|title="Aller Männerkultur zum Trotz": Frauen in Mathematik und Naturwissenschaften|author=Renate Tobies|publisher=Campus Verlag|year=1997|isbn=978-3-593-35749-2|pages=268–269}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|last=Johnson|first=Jeffrey A.|date=1998-12-01|title=German women in chemistry, 1925–1945 (part II)|journal=NTM International Journal of History & Ethics of Natural Sciences, Technology & Medicine|language=en|volume=6|issue=1|pages=65–90|doi=10.1007/BF02914207|pmid=27518333|s2cid=33178544|issn=1420-9144}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/BASFKarriere/status/974223731827658753|title=Eine weitere, bewundernswerte Frau in der #Geschichte von #BASF ist Dr. Emma Wolffhardt.|last=Karriere|first=BASF|date=2018-03-15|website=@BASFKarriere|language=de|access-date=2019-05-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|date=1974|title=Personal- und Hochschulnachrichten|journal=Nachrichten aus Chemie und Technik|language=en|volume=22|issue=13|pages=265–266|doi=10.1002/nadc.19740221310|issn=1868-0054}}</ref>。此外，她是第一個使用[[空間填充模型|空間填充模型]]來理解並改善[[有機合成|有機合成]]的科學家<ref name="Tobies1997" /><ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|last=Johnson|first=Jeffrey Allan|date=2013|title=The Case of the Missing German Quantum Chemists: On Molecular Models, Mobilization, and the Paradoxes of Modernizing Chemistry in Nazi Germany|journal=Historical Studies in the Natural Sciences|volume=43|issue=4|pages=391–452|doi=10.1525/hsns.2013.43.4.391|issn=1939-1811|jstor=10.1525/hsns.2013.43.4.391}}</ref>。曾就讀於[[維爾茨堡大學|維爾茨堡大學]]和[[卡爾斯魯厄理工學院|卡爾斯魯厄理工學院]]<ref name=":2" />。

